      <title>澳大利亚提高了今年的预测商品出口收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/australia-raises-forecast-commodity-export-income-for-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚增加了今年对商品出口收入的预测，但随着全球需求降低将价格降低，其降低的前景持续到本十年末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/australia-raises-forecast-commodity-export-income-for-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 13:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
